metadata.description:
Chasing Dreams  #1   1/1

The spirit of persistence, 
   The fire within.
It is in each of us,
    To pursue the win.
The perfect time is now,
    No time to wait.
Go into the wind,
    Swiftly out of the gate. 
    



Photography by N.M
Location: Smithsburg, MD    USA
